 Muhammad Kabir, Kano The ancient city of Kano has been thrown into mourning following the death in Cairo, Egypt  of the mother of the Emir of Kano, Aminu Ado Bayero, Maryam.
Palace sources hinted that Maryam Bayero had been sick for some weeks.
